      • LoadGame

        public void LoadGame(java.lang.String diraction)
        The method receives a CSV file address, and extracts necessary data from it to build a game. The method updates the appropriate drawings of fruits and pacmans on the screen.
        Parameters:
        diraction -

      • createGame

        public void createGame()
        The method takes data that the user puts on the screen and converts them into the game. Also creates a CSV file accordingly(output.csv).

      • runGame

        public void runGame()
        The method runs the game (thread)

      • runAlgo

        public void runAlgo()
        The method is part of the thread's run method. It runs the game and causes the pacman to move and "eat" the fruits. The Pacmans move according to their position at that point in time.
